ROLE BASED (coarse-grained):          PERMISSION BASED (fine-grained):
─────────────────────────────         ────────────────────────────────
ROLE_ADMIN  → can do everything       users:read
ROLE_USER   → limited access          users:write
ROLE_GUEST  → read only               orders:read
                                      orders:delete
